Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有實體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是幽靈嗎
