Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 這個不是IBN5100嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的老式PC
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一個月前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳言說它就沉睡在秋葉原的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這恐怕是聽說之後來打聽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來也沒找到
