Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終卻得出了「找不到就是不存在」的Final Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是這麼貴重的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發售時間距今有30年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時因為價格關係 誰都買不起PC
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就變得超級稀有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就寄信給你了 我是桐生萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:56.51,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}發信人：閃光的指壓師\N標題：我等你\N鳳凰院先生，立刻就發郵件給你了。\N我叫桐生萌郁! 二十歲!! 自由業者!!!\N以後再發郵件給你也沒問題吧!?\N就算你說不要我也會發的\N萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十歲 自由業者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說不要我也會發的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和剛剛那女人是同一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧沒有出賣你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是貴重的PC 很有可能並不在秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 久等了喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界糟糕了出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 真好吃啊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃點喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大學實驗室進行分析的結果表明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠蕉在分子層面上已經支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說香蕉已經變成了其他的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不糟糕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據現狀能想到的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到了電話烤箱（暫定）電磁波的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學狂人的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說毫無根據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 連接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那麼就用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:11.06,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉：真由喜的。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是真由氏的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「我」 用真由理提供的研究經費買的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說這是真由氏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 把整串都扔進去確認下變化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}常考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx40)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}通常考慮的簡稱。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根就夠了吧 常考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這麼點就能確認電話烤箱（暫定）的真正力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個括弧暫定囉嗦 趕緊去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在實驗上這麼小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法改變世界格局的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改變的也只有你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.74,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(909,630)}Cooling Off
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 緊急要求666 立刻發動冷嚴之封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府的批准？ 現在是說這事的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自導自演 辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你藏起來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.47,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(725,630)}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定是能夠進行瞬間轉移的電子烤箱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎麼可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又該如何說明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那一串香蕉上摘下 放到烤箱裡的香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠…蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 它是不是完整地接上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的確摘了一根吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.21,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(746,630)}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這果然…是瞬間轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做很有趣的實驗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部倫太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是叫鳳凰院凶真來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨…紅莉栖

